{"type": "article", "id": 50565, "title": "把便携风扇做成雪糕形状，看起来很清凉｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-02-25T22:57:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 48008, "name": "Pikka"}, {"id": 48009, "name": "RONG"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 48010, "name": "Christophe de Sousa"}, {"id": 48011, "name": "7 Nepo"}, {"id": 17376, "name": "Joe Doucet"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 153, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180225212109XJDAOCnUjxgYS6p3.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #222222} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Light Fragment Collection by Nendo</h3><p>1950 年代，日本艺术家野口勇设计了Akari 纸灯灯具系列，之后，这一系列灯具被 Vitra 设计博物馆收藏。最近，日本设计工作室 Nendo 以 Akari 系列为灵感开发了 Light Fragment 系列灯具。</p><p>野口勇把 Akari 系列形容为“发光雕塑”，而非照明设备。Nendo 的想法是做一些能够发光的碎片，手工雕刻的白色丙烯酸板呈现出从不透明、半透明到透明的状态。这些碎片包裹在一个透明的丙烯酸立方体中，还内置有一个 LED 铝管。来自 LED 的光线散发出来，显露出纸张般的形态。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212140FORoE5GaSp06XTVt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212140vjA3Z5JxIoWc7UDF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212140Rid4g8upVxWeyCl9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212140yDMxRYUtreLWu4dH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212140PBwIETvS0kaclNMG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212140E4GDQyYglwmqB2e6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/light-fragments/?erelease\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nendo</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Graphic Rugs by Joe Doucet</h3><p>纽约设计师 Joe Doucet 设计了一系列图形大胆的地毯，用实际行动支持居住在美国的跨性别者。</p><p>做这一系列的想法，是在去年特朗普宣布禁止跨性别者服兵役后产生的，与其合作的是地毯公司 Odabashian。一系列颜色鲜艳的图案地毯意在描绘美国的跨性别社区。</p><p>这一系列包括四种不同的设计，比如沿对角线分割开来的黄蓝条纹版本，不同程度的粉红色、橙色和红色构成的网格，纯白色背景下的黑色圆圈，以及绿松石色调下铺洒开来的红色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212409OzKHsDIq735Ar1Le.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212235xipMjFrqngOkLztl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709814\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212235v0a7ZgRbHpUkiTP9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212235U0vydjfTlE4MzOQW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714467\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.odabashian.com/collaborations\" rel=\"nofollow\">Odabashian</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Handyfan Popsicle by 7 Nepo</h3><p>炎热的夏日，吃一根冰棒是很爽的事儿，如果再来一点凉凉的风，那就更惬意了。韩国工业设计师 7 Nepo 将这二者结合在了一起，设计了一款雪糕形状的便携风扇，希望在燥热的夏日带给你由外及内的清凉与痛快。它有一个皮革手带，目的是便于携带，特别适合在夏季乘坐拥挤的公共交通工具的人士。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212459AF6kr5aRgd2X7zET.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.077344\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802252124591R8WqhGKs4HSwnZ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.632031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212459oY3PRfDg94GEZvyk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212459rvs20Gjn4o7B8YhI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212459DMAtgJObcmsFfvSL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.110156\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/61958637/Popsicle\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Bridge Desk by Christophe de Sousa</h3><p>AD CHALLENGE 17 挑战赛邀请了 15 位葡萄牙以及世界各地的设计师参与设计，要求是设计一件重视木材使用的作品。波尔图设计师 Christophe de Sousa 的作品是一张名为“桥”的书桌，灵感来源于他生活的城市波尔图，这是欧洲唯一一个拥有六座桥梁的城市。书桌可选橡木或者核桃木两种材质，两边的桌腿之间有一个铜片凹出来的弧度，意在表现桥梁结构。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212551m6eGzIpM07itfOoE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212551AgT8Dcx0fFtE49hw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212551Lpaj36rl5kDeNf7M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.110937\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802252125522xBY0s6IjdekWnPA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.110937\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://christophe-desousa-wa49.squarespace.com/bridge/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Christophe de Sousa</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Table Zoo by RONG</h3><p>上海创意设计工作室 RONG 推出了一个桌面创新文具产品系列 Table Zoo，设计通过提取小动物造型和姿态特质，将其与产品的功能性巧妙结合，打破常规文具产品冷淡沉闷的感受。青蛙伸长的舌头成了你拉开的胶带，刺猬的身体变成了图钉收纳盒，小鸟身体被插上了你画笔的彩色羽毛。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212630TjVf5YOg3oiBeblp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622917\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212631i5rbQqtPLg97KUEd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535417\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212631gsRmkSPIKvCc95tQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535417\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212631W3fCVZq408jQgKbk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212630SnZgsGr3WMCO80by.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535417\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212630uMOBqmniF8SvAdHf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212632RGyJpxQPCetvTiAz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.573958\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.rong-design.com/index.php?id=1830\" rel=\"nofollow\">RONG</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Circulum Shelf by Pikka</h3><p>钥匙、钱包、眼镜以及你认为类似的随身重要小物，一般回到家中你会将它们归置在哪？在下一次出门时是否又会慌忙中忘记放在了哪里？Circulum 搁板是一个解决方案，它可以从天花板上悬垂下来成为家中的一个装饰品，实用又优雅，最重要的是醒目，不会让你忘掉它的存在感。你可以将出门随身携带的重要小物件都归置在这个搁板上，出门时一目了然。售价 151 美元，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/raketas-circulum-pikka-05-23-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212730WYrvdCMumI9c4wik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212730ShpcEUj65dAvwB2L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212730XjsSfq9OkBIbAiPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802252127312tfCSv4uKxIVDQby.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212731zw5Rnd2yrxNQp7lZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212731SlJRm3hHGE1tbrje.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180225212730coj0Cm3vOlESBpxz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}